1. Purpose

Configure the libsharp library; see
<https://github.com/Libsharp/libsharp>.



From the web site:

Library for fast spherical harmonic transforms, see
<http://arxiv.org/abs/1303.4945>.

See also <https://arxiv.org/abs/1010.2084> for sYlm definitions and
conventions.
